#circuitbreakersg #lockdownhair #quarantinehaircut #johnwick #omjm

glass of drink instead of Katana,😄😄for sure! still looks like samurai

@paulopratienza haha am saying it as it is. . and yessss! I am looking forward coming up with more parties 🕺🏾
@ane.bakri you are the sweetest ane :) take care ok! we see eachother soon!

@mikeblanding oh, dont worry I am totally hating on it. 😂 just seeing how long i will ride this trashy look for haha
Hmmm... I was planning to hate on this. But I have to admit that... this is working.
@arbdaniele hahaha thanks Bill! Hi to francesca, and nono and nona! ❤️
@3.3_toffereism wahaha long hair na ba siya ngayon
@plant.man.dan dude i stole this from you 😂

@cabeaquino awww thanks Cabe! hope youre keeping well and safe
You should forever be on quarantine 😂🤣
